casebody.data:
STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Kareem T. TILLERY, a/k/a Kareem Ali Tillery, Kareem A. Tillery, Kareem J. Tillery, Karim Tillery, Kariem A. Tillery, Kareem Tillery-Jones and Kareem R. Jones, Defendant-Petitioner. C-512 September Term 2017
079832 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 26, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000682-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the appellant may serve and file a supplemental brief on or before March 27, 2018, and respondent may serve and file a supplemental brief forty-five (45) days after the filing of the appellant's supplemental submission, or, if appellant declines to file such a submission, on or before May 11, 2018.
